<:h1>Remesh Ramachandran</:h1>
<:p>Remesh Ramachandran, an Indian ethical hacker. Working on numerous cyber crimes, Ramachandran has engaged with Indian Government and International agencies. Ramesh is also a part of Google Hall of Fame. Ramesh has also worked with finance companies, conducting security audits.</:p>
<:p>Ramesh has worked as an independent consultant for Information security and infrastructure solutions. He then joined Hazdia group as IT security Manager. In the capacity of an advisory, Remesh also supports the EC council of the leading exam - Computer Hacking and Forensic Investigation (CHFI). He currently works with CISO.</:p>
<:p>- Google Hall of Fame spotting a bug known as Cross-site Scripting (XSS)</:p>
